{"title":"重绘家乡的蓝天","authors":["白朝蓉"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":11,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"重绘家乡的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白朝蓉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1998年夏，内蒙古呼、兴、哲盟及赤峰一带，发生了百年不遇的洪水灾害。秋末，我们来到这片重建家园的热土，所见所闻，可歌可泣，夜难成寐，遂吟小诗以颂之。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小康新村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是青石奠基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积淀的却是信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是红砖砌墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高筑的却是向往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是农家火炕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖的却是新梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长街杨柳成行时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自来水管喷泉时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电视天线传讯时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾民堆满皱纹的笑脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将是小康新村的旌旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连心石桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪魔用软鞭子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽断江河上的大桥小涵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔水相望的亲人啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像马头琴折了弓弦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用四肢作桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用脊骨作梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用肌肉铺路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用血液灌浆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥，多像同心结"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥，多像航天船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色长堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔下伐木斧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起植树锹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片林是一座水库"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一畦草是一曲水谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用沙袋石块"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镇压洪魔的肆虐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让田野阡陌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流淌温柔的涟漪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色灾难百年不遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色长堤千载不溃"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}